# Turbo Commands

- Use `turbo run <task>` to run workspace scripts.
- Add `--filter=<package>` when targeting a specific app/package.
- Use `pnpm` only for dependency management (install/add/remove/update).

Examples:
- `turbo run build --filter=web`
- `turbo run check`
- `pnpm add -D <pkg> -F web`
